{#
    ---
    title: Button Default
    ---

    Type: Atoms -> Buttons

    Description:
        There are three button styles for each Color Theme option: Primary, Secondary, and Tertiary. In general, buttons are used for actions that occur on the page, while links take users from one page to another. Depending on the importance of a link, you may decide to style it as a button to make it stand out more.
        
        The Default Button pattern supports both buttons and links. Links are created automatically if the button_default_href attribute is passed. If omitted, the resultant output will be a button element.

        To use one of the styles below, pass the "button_default_type" parameter the desired style ("primary", "secondary", "tertiary", or "negative").

        These button styles can also be applied to other button components by passing the desired classes (i.e. button--primary) to the pattern. See below for examples of using various button styles on other button components.

    Parameters:
        button_default_classes: Additional button classes.
        button_default_id: Button ID.
        button_default_type: Button style. Options: primary, secondary, tertiary, negative.
        button_default_label: Button text.
        button_default_href: Button link destination (optional).
        button_default_attributes: Additional button attributes.

    Last Updated: February 9, 2021
#}

{% set button_default_classes = button_default_classes|default() %}
{% set button_default_id = button_default_id|default() %}
{% set button_default_type = button_default_type|default() %}
{% set button_default_label = button_default_label|default() %}
{% set button_default_href = button_default_href|default() %}
{% set button_default_attributes = button_default_attributes|default() %}

<{{ button_default_href != "" ? 'a' : 'button' }} class="button-nds waves-effect waves-light button--{{ button_default_type }} {{ button_default_classes }}"{% if button_default_id is not empty %} id="{{ button_default_id }}"{% endif %}{% if button_default_href is not empty %} href="{{ button_default_href }}"{% endif %} role="button" {{ button_default_attributes|raw }}>{{ button_default_label }}</{{ button_default_href != "" ? 'a' : 'button' }}>